{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "74a1583f-6cf6-4d36-bc78-3339e9cbe05c", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/74a1583f-6cf6-4d36-bc78-3339e9cbe05c@1.pkg/1772597662968/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597663883", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/74a1583f-6cf6-4d36-bc78-3339e9cbe05c@1.pkg/1772597662968/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597663883"}, "identifier": "74a1583f-6cf6-4d36-bc78-3339e9cbe05c", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>②：依据教材知识，适度的焦虑情绪可以把压力转化为动力，如过度焦虑则会影响健康，故②知识性错误；</p>\n\n<p>①③：根据题干，转化了的积极情绪，有助于提升思考能力、学习效率等，故①③符合题意，</p>\n\n<p>故本题选B。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（原创）“公园20分钟效应”在2024年开始走红，网友们纷纷分享自己的“公园20分钟实践”表示该方式确实能舒缓压力，减少负面情绪，提高生活和工作效率。这启示我们（&nbsp; ）</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">①积极情绪能提高效率 &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">②人不可以有负面情绪</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">③要积极面对负面情绪 &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">④不如意时就要去公园</p>\n", "title": "（原创）“公园20分钟效应”在2024年开始走红，网友们纷纷分享自己的“公园20分钟实践”表示该方式确实能舒缓压力，减少负面情绪，提高生活和工作效率。这启示我们（  ）①积极情绪能提高效率  ②人不可以有负面情绪③要积极面对负面情绪  ④不如意时就要去公园", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/74a1583f-6cf6-4d36-bc78-3339e9cbe05c@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754826169484", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": []